
---
description: "Gate Pipeline(G0~G6) + Decision Rules"
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

- G0 STOP
- G1 Allowlist
- G2 Max Lines (add+del ≤ 300.00)
- G3 No Delete (0.00)
- G4 No Lockfile/Deps (0.00)
- G5 Commands PASS
- G6 DRY_RUN↔APPLY 일치

- AUTO_MERGE: G0~G6 PASS + risk=LOW + 승인
- PR_ONLY: soft fail(라인/lockfile/테스트)
- ZERO_STOP: STOP/allowlist 위반/삭제/외부전송/risk=HIGH+핵심 FAIL
